timelineItems.desc: Attempt saved. Juan Agudelo (New England Revolution) right footed shot from the center of the box is saved in the bottom left corner.

timelineItems.text: Not blue. Not green. He's somewhere in between! He's Teal. He's Teal! #NERevs

timelineItems.text: Scott Caldwell is an animal! Saves it with his head on a 2-1 break for Vancouver. Caldwell has been playing his heart out tonight #NERevs

timelineItems.name: Jake Catanese
timelineItems.text: @TealBunB with the wicked wrista and five-holes Ousted...I mean, that's a really good half-volley through traffic. #NERevs #NEvVAN

timelineItems.name: Justin Churchill
timelineItems.text: #NERevs playing better with an attacking focus. Only one DM on the field, but down to 10 Men #VWFC #MLS

timelineItems.name: Sean Sullivan
